TopicTitle: Eclipse I mission ends in Minor (Computer Overheat) Failure.

Articles.Content:
Well, My Eclipse I mission (To test how the launch escape system affects a normal mission, and to see the solar eclipse) ended in a minor failure, because it landed, then the computer overheated. There were no injuries.
